Package: terminaltiler
Version: 0.1.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: amd64
Maintainer: Zethrus
Depends: libc6 (>= @GLIBC_FLOOR@)
Description: Native tiling terminal workspace launcher
 TerminalTiler launches polished split-terminal workspaces with preset
 layouts, startup commands, and project-aware working directories.
 Runtime GTK, libadwaita, and VTE libraries are bundled inside the package.
